message.content: Based on the provided volatility data, the suspected payload of the initial exploit affecting the victim's bank account could be the file "sdra64.exe" located in \Device\HarddiskVolume1\WINDOWS\system32\. This file stands out as it is not a standard Windows system file and its presence in the system directory raises suspicion. Further analysis of this file, its behavior, and any associated network activity would be crucial to determine its malicious intent and impact on the victim's bank account.
